<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Perfect Air Service | HVAC Experts</title>

<style>
* {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
}

body {
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #333;
}

header {
    background: linear-gradient(to right, #0b4f9c, #1e88e5);
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 100px 20px;
}

header h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
}

header p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
}

.btn {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 25px;
    padding: 14px 28px;
    background: white;
    color: #0b4f9c;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-weight: bold;
}

.btn:hover {
    background: #f4f4f4;
}

section {
    padding: 60px 20px;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: auto;
}

h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    color: #0b4f9c;
}

.services {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 25px;
}

.card {
    background: #f8f9fa;
    padding: 25px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}

.card h3 {
    color: #0b4f9c;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
}

.about {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 800px;
}

.contact {
    text-align: center;
}

.phone {
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: #0b4f9c;
    font-weight: bold;
    margin: 20px 0;
}

footer {
    background: #222;
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 25px;
}

.highlight {
    color: #0b4f9c;
    font-weight: bold;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
    <h1>Perfect Air Service</h1>
    <p>Heating • Cooling • Repair • Maintenance • Replacement</p>
    <p>Serving Maryland, Virginia & Washington DC</p>
    <a href="#contact" class="btn">Call Now</a>
</header>

<section class="about">
    <h2>About Us</h2>
    <p>
        At <span class="highlight">Perfect Air Service</span>, we provide
        professional HVAC solutions throughout the DMV area. Whether you need
        a system replacement, emergency repair, or routine maintenance,
        we're committed to keeping your home comfortable year-round.
    </p>
</section>

<section>
    <h2>Our Services</h2>

    <div class="services">

        <div class="card">
            <h3>HVAC Repair</h3>
            <p>
                Fast and reliable repair services for air conditioners,
                furnaces, heat pumps, and complete HVAC systems.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h3>System Replacement</h3>
            <p>
                Upgrade your old HVAC equipment with modern,
                energy-efficient heating and cooling systems.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h3>Preventive Maintenance</h3>
            <p>
                Regular tune-ups and inspections to improve efficiency,
                lower energy costs, and prevent breakdowns.
            </p>
        </div>

    </div>
</section>

<section id="contact" class="contact">
    <h2>Contact Perfect Air Service</h2>

    <div class="phone">
        📞 240-516-9392
    </div>

    <p>Serving Maryland, Virginia & Washington DC</p>
    <p>Call today for service, maintenance, or a free replacement estimate.</p>
</section>

<footer>
    <p>© 2026 Perfect Air Service. All Rights Reserved.</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
